          },
          "type": "TEXT_INPUT",
          "options": [],
          "correctOptionIndex": null,
          "acceptedAnswers": [
            "54",
            "54 km/h",
            "54 km per hour"
          ],
          "hint": null,
          "wrongReason": {
            "english": "**Formula:** Average speed = Total distance ÷ Total time\n\n**Step 1:** Total distance = 324 km\n**Step 2:** Total time = 6 hours\n\n**Step 3:** Average speed = 324 ÷ 6 = **54 km/h**\n\nThis means the car covered 54 km every hour on average.\n\n**Answer: 54 km/h**",
            "hindi": "**Formula:** Average speed = Total distance ÷ Total time\n\n**Step 1:** Total distance = 324 km\n**Step 2:** Total time = 6 hours\n\n**Step 3:** Average speed = 324 ÷ 6 = **54 km/h**\n\nThis means the car covered 54 km every hour on average.\n\n**Answer: 54 km/h**"
          },
          "supportExample": {
